<xxl><c>Pango Markup</c></xxl>   

<b> Bold </b> <i> Italic </i>
Newlines preserve their meaning.
<hid>Hidden text is not shown.</hid>\

Backslash at the end of line \
is the continuation mark.
<span foreground='blue' size="50">Blue text</span> is <i>cool</i>
