<span background='green' size="50" italic=1 under=1 align=left> Green italic background </span> is <i>cool</i>
End of span.
<span foreground="red" size="40">Red text</span> is <i>un-cool</i>
<span foreground="green" size="20" align=center>Green centered text</span> is here.
Regular line of text.
Subscript text <sub>is here</sub> Back to regular. Superscript text <sup>is here</sup> 
Regular line of text.
Large <span size = 30>Subscript text <sub> is here</sub> Back to regular.</span>
Large <span size=30>Superscript text <sup>is here</sup> Regular again.</span> 
